# Project Name

My Blog

## Description

A blog website where users can view posts on various topics.

## Installation

1. Clone the repository
2. Install the required dependencies with the following command:

    ```python
    pip install -r requirements.txt
    ```

3. Run the application with the following command:

    ```python
    main.py
    ```

## Usage

1. Open a web browser and go to `<http://localhost:5000/>` to view all the available posts.
2. Click on the "Read" button to view the full post.
3. You can also navigate directly to a specific post by entering the post ID in the URL. For example, `<http://localhost:5000/post/1>` will show post number 1.

